name: Universe BooXx
description:
FINAL SERIES.

(((Thoughts Reminding)))

This series will take us to unknown situation that our brain always imagine inside the BooXx, this is the last series to close the 2021 and a part of Inside "Thoughts Universe Box" limited series.

Reminding for what that will happened, and what we do in the past.
reminding all the sins and balancing with some good things.
like a tree above the rain, rattles in the ceiling, maybe your bones inside the case, and these little heartbeats in the sea, until someone touch your inner sanctum sanctorum.
